Linda M. ELLIS, d.b.a Linda’s Lyrics, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. Eric J. ARONSON, Dash Systems, Inc., Defendants-Appellees. No. 05-13347

Non-Argument Calendar.

D.C. Docket No. 03-03086-CV-RWS-1. United States Court of Appeals, Eleventh Circuit. Dec. 6, 2005. Conrad M. Shumadine, Brett Alexander Spain, Gary Alvin Bryant, Willcox & Savage, P.C., Norfolk, VA, for Plaintiff-Appellant. Michael B. Butler, Law Offices of Michael B. Butler, P.C., Decatur, GA, for Defendants-Appellees. Before TJOFLAT, CARNES and PRYOR, Circuit Judges. PER CURIAM:

We find no merit in this appeal. The judgment of the district court is therefore

AFFIRMED.
